switch env {
case "production":
    // API endpoints: no scripts, no frames, self only
    config.CSPPolicy = "default-src 'none'; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'"
case "staging":
    config.CSPPolicy = "default-src 'self'; frame-ancestors 'none'"
}
```

3. **Security Monitoring Layer**:
```go
